snippet.title: MonsterBag Launch Trailer | PS Vita
snippet.description:
http://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/monsterbag-psvita/

Embark on an odyssey to reunite a monster bag and his owner Nia, while accidently starting an apocalypse along the way.
